703200f-a.text:
(1) Bergen Beach "Boardwalk", south of Aves W to X. This parak, was a place of amusement, ceased to exist, probably because of the raw sewage pumped into the Paerdegat Basin at the left.
April 1926.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, looking north from Royce Street to Ave. X.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
